Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【Main】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利的死讯很快传到了天城
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据哲力胥舰队来报 方修利确已死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将遵从殿下的命令 即日返航
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转告哲力胥卿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此行不辱使命 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.46,0:02:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥 你违背了对妈妈的誓言呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时 当时你说得那么好听…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是孩儿无能 没能生擒那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但母亲大人 请您务必保持冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.34,0:02:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我怎么能冷静得下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 尸体 尸体总有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要亲手把他碎尸万段 替亚瑟斯报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 很遗憾 尸体过后才能送来…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.54,0:02:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上掉头回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许你空手回来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是藩王殿下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个孩子 你这个孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:02:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个不孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1328,850)\fad(500,500)\fs90\bord4}艾斯塔尔的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗大人 据说方修利去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个战术家会这样轻易死去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 您是说他还活着？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想必正藏身于艾斯塔尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待时机逃往其它行星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗卿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙兰西亚 来信了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.69,0:03:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来法尔过得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他终于能独当一面了 可喜可贺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我想快点回信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没什么好话题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上准备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 要去工作吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然不知能不能作为信中话题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我有段时间会没法见公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥卿太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然没有考虑方修利还活着的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去负责遗体交接
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一方修利还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把他抓回来领功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于此事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗阁下主动请求负责交接
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藩王殿下已经批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他抢先了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 渚士朗卿的原副官正在卢塔西禁闭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说他身边不太平？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在先前的叛乱未遂事件中有人受到牵连
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说正怨恨着身为艾斯特拉德侯公子的法尔密子爵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以拿来做文章
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一处就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在官邸的警备配置上暗中开一个缺口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解渚士朗卿的为人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到原副官的死讯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能会辞掉此次任务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}惑星艾斯塔尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}惑星エスタール
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难缠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据情报显示
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔尔政府完全封锁了整个星球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连一只老鼠都逃不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让他们夸下海口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把提督的遗体交给泰坦尼亚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而关键的遗体不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若被我活着逃出了这个星球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这星球可真是万事休矣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想听到什么「大概能」之类
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们真能逃出去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早预料到了这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警戒早晚会放松的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 反正我们有得是储备粮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的巧克力可能会剩下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直觉罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉机会可能很快就会来临
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}法尔密子爵府
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}バルアミー子爵邸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讽刺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到居然会被伊德里斯卿的部下保护
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的生活也很无聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主也很担心你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提起公主 她已经在信上写了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说会没法见到渚士朗卿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也想通知你一声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思 我也想同往的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 还请多多当心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔密卿！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 法尔密卿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔密卿！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔密卿只受了点擦伤 逃过一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手下当场逮捕了不逞之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方无疑是叛乱份子的残党
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详情正在调查中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在您的管辖之下居然会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是警卫人手不足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太失礼了 我方的警备是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后会加强戒备…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗卿？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会向藩王殿下提议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此次事件为戒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,争取解除法尔密卿的紧闭处分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请派他作为和艾斯塔尔的交涉辅佐同往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且在适当的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照伊德里斯卿先前的提议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派他前往周边星域赴任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是比禁闭更重的发配边疆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样既能保证他的人身安全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不会给伊德里斯卿添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这确实是我提议的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但渚士朗卿是不信任我的部队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有那种意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若殿下不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事就交给你处理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 同意渚士朗卿的提议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的计划居然全盘落空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于渚士朗卿从中斡旋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔密再次回到了宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副官大人 别来无恙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗卿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用说客套话了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此事结果加重了你受的处分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我擅自主张 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经有所觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起身上开个洞 这算不了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗卿之所以要去艾斯塔尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若只需确认遗体的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗卿和法尔都走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人 还请暂且忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位很快都会回天城的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道是知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是会寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直陪着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙兰西亚 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}埃尔伯特·卡纳库大总统
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エルベルト・カナック大統領
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 泰坦尼亚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙 这么快就等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是情报泄漏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有相关迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.59,0:11:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但下官担心对方舰队会发现我方的动向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是著名的智将渚士朗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若被他抓住马脚就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问如何处置？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 马上解除舰队对星球的封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样一来 万一被方修利逃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续封锁宇宙港
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若有船从其它地方逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是方修利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然不知道他本人是死是活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 下官马上去办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备一口棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况有变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么新动向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚的舰队马上会来取提督的遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔尔政府急忙解除了封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 不出所料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 是谁来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗·泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是四公爵中最有心计的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督和他谁更有心计
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是我的研究题目之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有心计吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很讨厌这个对手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但毕竟机不可失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽力而为吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能顺利交接吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据对方的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计会有一番辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥卿做得也真过火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来会拖入持久战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔密卿就按计划行事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:13:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}艾斯塔尔大总统官邸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エスタール大統領官邸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡纳库大总统阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然在下来得突然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但您还是抽空接见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳烦渚士朗卿亲自前来 不胜光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也看到那副惨状了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在贵方谢罪之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上我国的尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会和泰坦尼亚握手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理解贵国的主张了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望在交涉之前能先确认遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 关于移送天城一事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您不要误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先前确实谈妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但哲力胥卿后来攻击我国 扬长而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若贵国不对侵略我国主权进行道歉和赔偿…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不移交遗体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我并不是为谢罪而来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就没必要谈了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 并不是全无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揣测交涉对象的气量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这点来说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太无礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖延时间才是阁下的本意所在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.75,0:15:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵国的宇宙港为什么封锁着？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利一派还有残党
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要瞒着我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有义务告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么要动用军队？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗卿 请快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说艾斯塔尔军发现了方修利的藏身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了祖国
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜祭出空城计争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于您的信念 在下拜服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大总统阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的苍蝇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.37,0:16:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要抓住方修利…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次真是永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来没这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗正在艾斯塔尔交涉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方群龙无首 总会有办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然和传言中一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰散开 封锁目标的退路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮第二次齐射 瞄准完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威慑攻击 不要命中了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:17:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让对方停船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔尔舰队从前方快速接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前门拒虎 后门进狼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来虎和狼的关系不太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔尔舰队发来通信表示抗议
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标减速了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吧 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要停船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想仔细看看对方的船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他呢 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 若没有我在 就只能全力逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 被抓住只有死路一条
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有我在船上 减速也就有了意义
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是投降 或是献上我乞求饶命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗·泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不会不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他三七二十一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有赌在逮捕我的瞬间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓破绽 都发生在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放他走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 渚士朗卿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利多半还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要确认这一点就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他是泰坦尼亚的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是泰坦尼亚的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚时刻需要有敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此事事关泰坦尼亚安泰和繁荣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰 停止攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方收起了武器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不打算开火吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.43,0:21:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要放我们一条生路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会从背后「砰」的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.13,0:21:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗卿和方修利提督
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 青史留名的二人首次意识到了彼此的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.57,0:24:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家似乎都因为我年轻而小觑我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.98,0:24:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有人知道我的悲惨经历吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.56,0:24:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终有一天 要让卿等都拜倒在我的脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.03,0:24:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(693,290)\fad(500,0)\fs90\bord5}野望的前奏曲


